cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses a novel approach to meta-learning for one/few shot classification, which involves using a feed-forward embedding, attention mechanism, and deeper CNN embedding. These techniques are commonly used in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
